title: Fed’s Paulson Says Additional Rate Cuts Possible Later This Year
description: Federal Reserve Bank of Philadelphia President Anna Paulson said modest additional interest-rate cuts could be appropriate later in 2026, but conditioned that outcome on a benign outlook for the economy.
